      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a \"single day\" though. it's everything. i look at them and i just see how much my mistakes and my constant struggle affect them. it's like i'm just a shadow over their lives. i can see the stress on their faces and it just makes me think they'd be so much happier if they didn't have to deal with me anymore.",
